From: vabhasin <69602923+vabhasin@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Jun 2026 17:00:50 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] Release v1.18.2 (#2329)

* Add minimum length validation for stun ERROR_CODE parsing (#2305)

* Fix packet length validation in handleDcepPacket (#2312)

* fix constant used for stap B h264 packet (#2314)

* Add packet length checks for h264 and h65 RTP packet (#2317)

* Add bound check for candidate length in deserializeRtcIceCandidateInit (#2315)

* Add bounds check before reading recvDelta in TWCC packet (#2318)

* bump the version to 1.18.2
